{"type":null,"faqId":44822,"title":"如何查看所有的情景智能提醒？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">请确认情景智能已打开。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">打开通知栏，点击通知栏右上角的</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161793\" style=\"width:0.45833334in;height:0.46875in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s1\">，进入情景智能提醒中心。然后可以查看当前的提醒。当有特殊提醒出现时，</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161794\" style=\"width:0.45833334in;height:0.46875in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s1\">将变为特殊提醒图标。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">在提醒中心点击屏幕右上角的</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161795\" style=\"width:0.35347223in;height:0.25694445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s1\">，可查看历史提醒。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"323","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409267000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":3,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"情景智能,设置,生日提醒","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}